data.description: Amazing two Story 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in White Rock estates. This home has curb appeal and so much more. The primary bedroom is located on the main floor along with the laundry room, office/formal living formal dining and family room. Upstairs is where you will find three quality size bedrooms all with over sized closets and additional space for the kids or a he/she room. This home has a new roof, recess lighting, covered front and back porch, full sprinkler system, crown molding throughout to include laundry room plantation shutters, wrought iron railing, 2 car garage, Custom lighting , large shed and so much more. One owner that took amazing pride in the care of their home. Don't miss out , call for a showing. The seller will contribute towards closing.
